AIE: PCI-DSS: DB Account Auth Failure Alert Rule
CommonEvent.ShortDesc: AIE: This AIE Rule alerts on the occurrence of any database authentication failure from unauthorized accounts in direct support of PCI-DSS controls 10.2.1, 10.2.4 and in supplemental support of PCI-DSS Controls: 8.7.a, 8.7.c-d.

CommonEvent.Name: AIE: PCI-DSS: Invalid Act Auth Failure Alert Rule
CommonEvent.ShortDesc: AIE: This AIE Rule alerts on the occurrence of any authentication failure attempts from unauthorized accounts (default /disabled/terminated) in direct support of PCI-DSS Controls: 2.1.b/10.1/10.2.1-.2/10.2.4; supplemental support of 8.1.3.a/8.1.4/8.5.c

CommonEvent.Name: AIE: PCI-DSS: Priv Acct Auth Failure Alert Rule
CommonEvent.ShortDesc: AIE: This AIE Rule alerts on the occurrence of any authentication failure attempt from privileged accounts in direct support of PCI-DSS Controls: 10.1, 10.2.1, 10.2.2, 10.2.4, 10.2.5.a and augmented support of 7.1.1

CommonEvent.Name: AIE: PCI-DSS: Vendor Auth Failure Alert Rule
CommonEvent.ShortDesc: AIE: This AIE Rule alerts on the occurrence of any vendor account use of remote access in direct support of PCI-DSS Controls: 10.2.1 & 10.2.4 and in supplemental support of PCI-DSS Controls: 8.1.5.a, 8.1.5.b, 8.1.6.b, 12.3.9

CommonEvent.Name: AIE: GPG-13: Auth Failure on Intrnl Boundary Dvc
CommonEvent.ShortDesc: AIE: This AIE Rule creates an event and alerts on authentication failures on any internal boundary monitoring device to supplement testing of GPG-13 control PMC5.3 [Alert B].

CommonEvent.Name: AIE: GPG-13: Remote Access Auth Failure
CommonEvent.ShortDesc: AIE: This AIE Rule creates an event and alerts on any authentication failure activity originating from a remote access point to supplement testing of GPG-13 control PMC6.1 [Alert A].

CommonEvent.Name: AIE: GPG-13: VPN Node Registration Failure (author
CommonEvent.ShortDesc: AIE: This AIE Rule creates an event and alerts on any unsuccessful Virtual Private Network (VPN) node registration attempt into the boundary to supplement testing of GPG-13 control PMC6.2 [Alert A] for authorized VPN users (list).

CommonEvent.Name: AIE: GPG-13: Network Auth Failure
CommonEvent.ShortDesc: AIE: This AIE Rule creates an event and alerts on any authentication failure activity against a network connection console at the boundary to supplement testing of GPG-13 control PMC6.8 [ Alert B].

CommonEvent.Name: AIE: ISO-27001: Priv Act Auth Failure Rule

CommonEvent.Name: AIE: ISO-27001: Term Act Auth Failure Rule
CommonEvent.ShortDesc: AIE: This AIE Rule creates an alert and provides details on terminated account authentication failure activity (login failure).

CommonEvent.Name: AIE: ISO-27001: Vendor Act Auth Fail
CommonEvent.ShortDesc: AIE: This AIE Rule creates an alert and provides details on vendor account authentication failure activity (login failure).

CommonEvent.Name: AIE: ISO-27001: VPN Node Registration Failure Rule
CommonEvent.ShortDesc: AIE: This AIE Rule creates an event and alerts on any unsuccessful Virtual Private Network (VPN) node registration attempt into the environment.

CommonEvent.Name: AIE: GPG-13: VPN Node Reg Failure (un-Auth)
CommonEvent.ShortDesc: AIE: This AIE Rule creates an event and alerts on any unsuccessful Virtual Private Network (VPN) node registration attempt into the boundary by un-authorized users.

CommonEvent.Name: AIE: NERC-CIP: VPN Node Registration Fail (Auth)
CommonEvent.ShortDesc: AIE: This AIE Rule creates an event and alerts on any unsuccessful Virtual Private Network (VPN) node registration attempt into the Electronic Security Perimeter for authorized VPN users (list).

CommonEvent.Name: AIE: NERC-CIP: VPN Node Registration Fail (unAuth)
CommonEvent.ShortDesc: AIE: This AIE Rule creates an event and alerts on any unsuccessful Virtual Private Network (VPN) node registration attempt into the Electronic Security Perimeter for accounts not authorized as indicated within the authorized VPN users list
